or\" -newer /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/EntityList.razor -exec ls -lh {} \\;\n\ncat << 'EOF'\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------\n三、技术特性\n----------------------------------------------------------------\n\n✅ 使用 Blazor WebAssembly\n✅ 调用已有的 26 个 API 接口\n✅ 使用 Bootstrap 5 样式\n✅ 包含完整的 CRUD 功能\n✅ 友好的用户界面\n✅ 响应式设计\n✅ 表单验证\n✅ 分页功能\n✅ 搜索过滤\n✅ 模态对话框\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------\n四、页面路由映射\n----------------------------------------------------------------\n\n/                      → Home.razor\n/login                 → Login.razor\n/register              → Register.razor\n/entities              → EntityList.razor\n/entities/create       → EntityCreate.razor\n/entities/{id}         → EntityDetail.razor\n/entities/{id}/data    → EntityData.razor\n/forms                 → FormList.razor\n/forms/{id}/design     → FormDesigner.razor\n/forms/{id}/preview    → FormPreview.razor\n/workflows             → WorkflowList.razor\n/workflows/{id}/design → WorkflowDesigner.razor\n/workflows/my-tasks    → WorkflowTasks.razor\n/admin/users           → UserManagement.razor\n/admin/roles           → RoleManagement.razor\n/admin/plugins         → PluginManagement.razor\n/admin/tenants         → TenantManagement.razor\n/notifications         → NotificationList.razor\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------\n五、更新内容\n----------------------------------------------------------------\n\n✅ 更新 NavMenu.razor - 添加所有新页面的导航链接\n✅ 支持分类导航（数据管理、表单设计、工作流、系统管理）\n✅ 添加通知徽章显示\n\n================================================================\n任务完成时间：$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n执行部门：工部\n================================================================\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1472,"output":965,"cacheRead":63744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66181,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"tot